  <h1>Pancakes</h1>
  <img src="https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/AOmpz3ts_5t2VfXtOnJMSF7fWXA=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/21014-good-old-fashioned-pancakes-mfs-74-4x3-9ab7320540044d1bb881b259c7dfb258.jpg" alt="Pancakes" width="400">

  <h2>Description</h2>
  <p>Fluffy pancakes are a breakfast favorite. They're quick to whip up and perfect with maple syrup or fresh fruit.</p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>1 1/2 cups flour</li>
    <li>3 1/2 tsp baking powder</li>
    <li>1 tsp salt</li>
    <li>1 tbsp sugar</li>
    <li>1 1/4 cups milk</li>
    <li>1 egg</li>
    <li>3 tbsp butter, melted</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Mix dry ingredients in a bowl.</li>
    <li>Add milk, egg, and butter; mix until smooth.</li>
    <li>Pour batter onto a hot griddle.</li>
    <li>Cook until bubbles form, then flip.</li>
    <li>Serve warm with syrup or toppings.</li>
  </ol>

